<!-- Public assets directory -->

This folder contains static assets that are publicly accessible.

## What goes here:
- resume.pdf - Your resume (download)
- favicon.ico - Browser tab icon
- Images (if hosting locally)
- Any other static files

## Resume Setup:
1. Convert your resume to PDF
2. Name it "resume.pdf"
3. Place it in this folder
4. It will be accessible at: /resume.pdf

## Important:
- Keep files organized
- Compress images (use TinyPNG)
- Only include necessary files
- Don't commit node_modules here
